  "text": "Proving Cache Coherence. We first consider the version german-cache which has been widely used in many previous works [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] among others and then consider the extended system german-cache-fifo. In both cases, the cache coherence property to prove is ∀i, j : cache(i) = exclusive ∧i = j ⇒ cache( j ) = invalid. All the experiments are performed on an 2.1 GHz Pentium machine running Linux with 1GB of RAM.",
